data.description: Looking for a stylish condominium in the heart of the vibrant and upscale Atlantic Station? Look no further! This beautiful haven boasts an open living room/ kitchen, adorned with sleek stainless steel appliances and solid surface counters.  The perfect space for entertaining loved ones.  2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, spacious master bath with a tiled separate shower, and double vanities!  But that's not all, as part of the community association you will have full access to the fitness facilities and the luxury inground pool on those hot summer days.  Looking for a place to relax and soak in the city after a long day?  step out on your beautiful private patio!  This is a ground unit so easy access as well!  Schedule an appointment today this won't last!
